{"type":"message","id":"bde34cd8","parentId":"2a7b4a07","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:57:40.369Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sqzl0dbodv19_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4076\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=637\n[file inferred from ACTION] research/CFI_HYBRID_EXPERIMENT.md\n[mutation proposed] research/CFI_HYBRID_EXPERIMENT.md\n[master ef70dfd] pulse: 2026-03-24 155714\n 6 files changed, 229 insertions(+), 95 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 155714.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 155714.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 155617.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 155714 - The CFI compression synthesis identified that binary thresholds fail due to constant-format tokens (freq�160, CFI=1.0). A hybrid scoring formula was proposed: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120). This needs empirical validation."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"rapid-mist","total":10,"totalLines":10,"totalChars":782,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774382260368}}
